sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Person
  participant App as Frontend/Admin
  participant KC as Keycloak
  participant API as Backend service
  participant DB as Service-owned DB
  Person->>App: Open protected flow
  App->>KC: OIDC login
  KC-->>App: Access and refresh tokens
  App->>API: Bearer token API request
  API->>API: Validate issuer/JWK/roles/tenant context
  API->>DB: Read/write owned data
  DB-->>API: Result
  API-->>App: Response
